check: 4. Strict Completion Envelope validation and composed delivery
verdict: FAIL
boundary: Parent-boundary schema validation and composed reviewer delivery are reported separately. Direct mock runs prove the staged validator's behavior; composed runs cross the wrapper with a read-only policy granting only that run's capture path. A parent PASS cannot mask a composed delivery defect.
unresolved-risk: The parent validator passes, but a reviewer cannot reliably deliver the required envelope through the composed pi-subagents/Landstrip boundary.
